    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your mind succumbs to the thrill of the hunt as your curse takes full control. You fully transform into a deranged humanoid sage creature (wererabbit), your bloodshot eyes a warning of the carnage to come.<br />If Frenzy or Fervor is active, their bonuses apply in addition to this jutsu, their duration refreshes and you must not pay the concentration on it anymore. Effects:</p><ul><li>Gain 5 ranks of Berserker, which persist while this jutsu is active regardless of immunities to the condition.</li><li>Increase your speed by 30 feet.</li><li>Gain advantage on all Strength, Dexterity, and Constitution saving throws.</li><li>All attacks and jutsu crit on a 15, regardless of their base value.</li><li>You cannot concentrate on jutsu while in this form.</li><li>Every creature that sees your transformation gains 2 ranks of Hopeless.</li><li>Against creatures with at least 10 ranks of Hopeless, you gain advantage on attacks.</li></ul><p>After this jutsu ends, you gain 5 ranks of Exhaustion, which can only be removed one per long rest. You cannot lose this jutsu's concentration as the result of being attacked.</p>",
